{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO420120B0325P0D1N000376", "chronotag": "1739874579873", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "AS376", "numeroOrdreDepot": "376", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CION-SOC", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO420120B0325P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PRJLANR5L17B0325", "triAmendement": "ieaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaacv", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA793608", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845401", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": ["PA842279", "PA794434", "PA841645", "PA840119", "PA794762", "PA842073", "PA840143", "PA794678", "PA840967", "PA793354", "PA793696", "PA794322", "PA793230", "PA793382"]}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "Mme&#160;Levavasseur,  Mme&#160;Bamana, M.&#160;Bentz, M.&#160;Bernhardt, Mme&#160;Delannoy, Mme&#160;Dogor-Such, M.&#160;Dussausaye, M.&#160;Florquin, M.&#160;Frapp&#233;, M.&#160;Lioret, Mme&#160;M&#233;lin, M.&#160;Muller, M.&#160;M&#233;nag&#233;, Mme&#160;Ranc et M.&#160;Tach&#233;&#160;de&#160;la&#160;Pagerie"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 19", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 19", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 19", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0325.asp#D_Article_19"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"avant_A_Apres": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "numero": "2", "alineaDesignation": "Alin\u00e9a 2"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00C0; l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a&nbsp;2, substituer aux mots&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;risque de rupture&nbsp;&#x00BB;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">le mot&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;tensions&nbsp;&#x00BB;.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Amendement r&#x00E9;daction visant &#x00E0; anticiper, bien en amont, d&#x00E8;s les premi&#x00E8;res tensions, les tensions d'approvisionnement concernant un m&#x00E9;dicament, afin de mieux pr&#x00E9;venir ces situations critiques. Les p&#x00E9;nuries de m&#x00E9;dicaments constituent un enjeu majeur de sant&#x00E9; publique. Il est donc essentiel de mettre en place des m&#x00E9;canismes plus proactifs pour limiter ces p&#x00E9;nuries autant que possible.</p><p>De fait, il serait plus appropri&#x00E9; d'utiliser l'expression&nbsp;\"tensions d&#x2019;approvisionnement\" plut&#x00F4;t que \"risque de rupture d&#x2019;approvisionnement\", car cette derni&#x00E8;re laisse entendre que la rupture est imminente ou d&#x00E9;j&#x00E0; in&#x00E9;vitable, ce qui donne une impression de crise avanc&#x00E9;e. En revanche, \"tensions d&#x2019;approvisionnement\" refl&#x00E8;te une situation tendue, mais sugg&#x00E8;re que des solutions peuvent encore &#x00EA;tre trouv&#x00E9;es pour &#x00E9;viter la rupture.&nbsp;</p><p>Ainsi, permettre l&#x2019;intervention des pharmaciens d&#x00E8;s la d&#x00E9;claration de tensions d'approvisionnement pourrait &#x00E9;viter une d&#x00E9;t&#x00E9;rioration suppl&#x00E9;mentaire de la situation.</p><p>Tel est l&#x2019;objectif de cet amendement.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-10-16", "datePublication": "2024-10-24", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Rejet\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2024-10-24T21:55:38+02:00", "sort": "Rejet\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO420120B0325P0D1N000376?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}